Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.94,0:01:49.10,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是戀愛諮詢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.46,0:01:53.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我也不知道怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:58.97,Kaguya_hm_title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,400)\bord4\fs75\pos(1402,890)}輝夜大小姐想做到底
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:56.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說學生會也能做這類諮詢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.24,0:01:59.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,只有輝夜大小姐能幫我了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.36,0:02:01.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:06.00,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,傾聽同學煩惱也是學生會的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:08.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會長也總把這掛在嘴邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:12.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 是怎樣的戀愛煩惱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:16.81,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道能和男朋友圓滿分手的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:19.68,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:23.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為是兩三階段之前的諮詢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.65,0:02:27.54,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,關於有男朋友的女生的諮詢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.05,0:02:29.85,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,輝夜大小姐您這麼受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:32.42,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定有豐富的戀愛知識
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:33.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還如此沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:36.99,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有戀愛經驗的我怎麼可能回答得出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:36.21,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,您一定能給我非常合適的建議
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.54,0:02:39.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,對我的期待也太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.03,0:02:45.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,然而作為四宮一族的人一言既出駟馬難追
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.57,0:02:47.05,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,只能想辦法渡過難關了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:49.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你想要分手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:53.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為他突然對我告白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.26,0:02:57.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我就順勢答應他了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.98,0:03:00.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我其實並不了解他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:02.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道要怎麼對待他才好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.96,0:03:05.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不如說比交往前隔閡還深
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.68,0:03:08.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得很對不起他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:11.70,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會分手了反而更好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:16.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:19.51,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,因為在交往前你們完全是陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:22.57,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你會有這樣的感覺也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.38,0:03:25.34,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你並不是討厭他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.84,0:03:26.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.19,0:03:31.46,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但我也不知道這到底算不算是愛情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:36.27,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 從發現他的優點開始如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.66,0:03:37.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,找到喜歡他的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:41.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 無論是誰都會有優點或是惹人喜愛的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:49.00,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,比如說 他做事認真 成績優異 努力上進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.34,0:03:53.52,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,或是十分善良 從不拋棄有困難的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:57.34,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,又或者是眼神比較兇惡之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:04:00.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,眼神兇惡不是缺點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:04.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是呢 他在意自己眼神兇惡這點就可愛死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:07.78,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,您喜歡眼神兇惡的男生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:09.32,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才說的你都忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:12.70,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要說輝夜大小姐身邊眼神兇惡的人就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:16.16,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有這回事 我們繼續談吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.76,0:04:20.78,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,發現他的優點 從一個優點喜歡上他開始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:23.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你就會發現他有很多長處
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.44,0:04:26.58,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,等回過神來你就無法從他身上移開視線
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:28.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,如果每天都盯著他看…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:31.54,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就會慢慢喜歡上他本人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:34.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我的朋友是這麼跟我說的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:35.97,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不是我說的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.82,0:04:37.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,誒居然不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.07,0:04:40.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.29,0:04:42.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我又沒有喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:44.26,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是剛才說的那些…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:46.44,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,事情我大概了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:47.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:50.89,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不讓我一起加入戀愛話題實在太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:55.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這種話題請交給本人「戀愛偵探千花」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.66,0:04:58.54,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼氣喘吁吁的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:01.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我更早前就已經在這兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:03.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但又跑去戲劇部一趟換了身衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:08.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你對無法明白對他的想法而感到煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:09.68,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:10.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:13.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那名為「戀愛」的遺失品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.90,0:05:16.95,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就由我這個名偵探來幫你找到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:22.17,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來 請想像一下那個男生與別的女生親熱的場景
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:23.80,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:25.92,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,總之就先想像一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:34.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,煩躁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:36.17,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,氣憤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.14,0:05:41.02,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,總感覺很不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:42.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:44.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,換而言之那就是所謂「嫉妒」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:48.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,因為喜歡他才會覺得不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:52.78,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,越是覺得不舒服就越是愛得深沉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:54.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:55.46,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,Love？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:57.94,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧 這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:59.69,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我認為柏木同學是喜歡你的男朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:06:02.63,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼可能對會長抱有這樣的感情 不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:02.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,只要慢慢培養這份感情就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:03.84,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:07.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為自己是無法喜歡上向我告白的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:10.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是那樣冷酷無情的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:11.97,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:15.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 我一定是喜歡著他的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.13,0:06:17.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺已經快得出結論了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:24.18,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼樣才能更自然地跟男朋友聊天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:24.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要給出一些合適的建議才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:26.05,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,關於這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.89,0:06:28.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,「認知平衡」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:31.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以試試利用「羅密歐與朱麗葉效應」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.18,0:06:34.09,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,羅密歐與朱麗葉？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.18,0:06:34.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,羅密歐與朱麗葉？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:37.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,羅密歐與朱麗葉的愛情受到阻撓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:40.48,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,因為共同面對強大的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:43.42,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他們愛得更深
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:46.48,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,強大的敵人是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:48.72,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不一定是人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:51.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有共同的假想敵就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:53.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可沒有這樣的假想敵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:57.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不 每個人都有不得不面對的強大敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:06:59.54,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:01.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.95,0:07:03.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這個社會本身！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.38,0:07:05.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,社會？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:08.46,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,永不停止的戰爭 永不消除的貧富差距
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:10.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有比這更強大的敵人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:12.37,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,誒等等 應該是測試或者煩惱之類的小事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:17.52,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 只要二人齊心反抗這腐敗的社會就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:18.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,規模太大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:22.03,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂了 我們這就去做好準備
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:23.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.18,0:07:24.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊我說 你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:30.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係嗎 我們真的沒有創造出新的反社會分子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:34.00,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.48,0:07:39.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,請大家幫幫忙籌款
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:41.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:44.93,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,請大家幫幫忙籌款
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:46.82,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:47.64,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,他們倆原本就對慈善活動有興趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:50.23,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎成了不錯的契機
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:52.66,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,祈願和平的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.98,0:07:57.11,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也許這才是真正意義上的反抗社會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.47,0:07:58.41,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:03.80,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,她的男朋友是來找會長諮詢過的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:10.91,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.64,0:08:13.91,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:16.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會長會參加這個活動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:20.50,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 因為我接到校外籌款活動的申請
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.03,0:08:24.79,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,請大家幫幫忙籌款
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:27.24,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:25.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 我看他們既不是一時興起也不像是在打發時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:31.13,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,請大家幫幫忙籌款
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:33.46,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:28.68,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,看著雖然沒經驗但努力的他們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:32.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然力量微薄但不知不覺想幫他們一把
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.31,0:08:38.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 這種活動根本不適合我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.11,0:08:43.92,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你的這點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:45.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今日戰局
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.34,0:08:48.03,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,輝夜的敗北
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:51.97,Kaguya_hm_miaowu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\c&H484447&\fs70\b0\pos(1905,15)\fad(200,0)}請\N大\N家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:51.97,Kaguya_hm_miaowu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\c&H484447&\fs70\b0\pos(1845,15)\fad(200,0)}幫\N幫\N忙\N籌\N款
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:51.97,Kaguya_hm_miaowu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\c&H484447&\fs70\b0\pos(1785,15)\fad(200,0)}拜\N托\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:56.80,Kaguya_hm_title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,400)\bord4\fs85\pos(446,902)}白銀御行想耍耍威風
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.33,0:09:11.88,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就差一點點！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:13.55,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,運動白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.81,0:09:17.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,白銀雖然非常擅長學習
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:21.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,然而關於運動方面真的是毀滅級別的不擅長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:25.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,長年的送報紙 暑假的搬家打工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:29.27,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就連每天騎15公里單車上學都輕鬆完成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:33.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,白銀御行絕不是身體素質不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:38.14,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,而是令人絕望地不擅長體育運動 這就是原因
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:41.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,他要繼續保持他在秀知院學園的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:44.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就需要持之以恆地訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:47.54,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,下週有排球課
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:50.99,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須得達到普通人的級別才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:53.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要是這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:55.15,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,請你認真點行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:58.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 那個像快死一樣的羊駝的是會長？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:09:58.95,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:00.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那個快死一樣的羊駝？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:04.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:06.21,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:10.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼怎樣都不順利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:13.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:14.99,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 沒問…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:16.52,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原書記
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:18.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:21.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘了東西在這兒 就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.88,0:10:22.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,被看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:25.14,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那個蠢得不行的動作被看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:27.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:31.01,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,文武雙全 萬事精通的白銀會長的招牌…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:36.23,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,明明啥都沒幹但是什麼都會的我這一印象…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:39.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,考前複習？沒怎麼做過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:40.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:45.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,球真好玩兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:46.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,哎隨便了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.39,0:10:49.78,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,她怎麼看我我也不太受傷就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.57,0:10:52.84,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,下次不是會有排球課嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:55.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,因為能借到體育館 所以我在練習
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:57.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不太擅長發球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:11:00.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:02.49,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意的話我來教你吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:07.51,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你啊 要教別人首先你自己得會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:10.51,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我區區排球還是會打的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:11.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:14.81,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:16.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:18.60,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,多麼利落的發球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:19.88,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得咋樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.05,0:11:22.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,沒 沒想到你會有這樣的絕技
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:28.21,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我來教你 你肯定一下就上手了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:34.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長 請人教你的時候要用什麼態度呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:39.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,請 請你教教我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:42.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.29,0:11:45.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們就先來找找問題出在哪兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.84,0:11:48.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,請你發幾次球給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:49.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:52.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:54.46,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:11:57.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯——？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.23,0:12:03.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:04.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:08.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不管打幾次都會打到自己的頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.43,0:12:09.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,太注意自己的頭的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:11.32,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,又抓不住時機
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:14.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,完全陷入僵局了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:16.11,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:19.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 打球的時候要把眼睛睜開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.81,0:12:21.55,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是當然的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:23.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就是呀 就是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:26.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以這次把眼睛睜大再試一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:28.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣怎麼可能有變化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:32.51,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:37.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 沒用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:38.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有睜眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:40.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有睜開眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.43,0:12:41.66,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹嘛擺出一副
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.67,0:12:43.26,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,「按你說的做了 但還是不行」的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:46.16,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 一毫米都沒睜開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:47.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:51.34,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,難道這就是傳說中的易普症
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.44,0:12:52.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你是白痴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:57.14,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是會長自己的想法和動作不協調
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:13:00.21,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,先從跳的時候睜眼開始練習
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:03.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要徹底改正過來 做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:04.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:06.89,Kaguya_zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs70\c&H393737&\3c&HF5F4F2&\b1}魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:06.02,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:12.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,1 2 3 4 5
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:15.68,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,556 557 558 559
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.70,0:13:18.49,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,984 985 986
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:18.05,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,跳的時候不要閉眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:22.42,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,從早到晚特訓三天後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:22.23,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,球是最好的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.94,0:13:26.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.42,0:13:29.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:32.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經和普通人的差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:36.59,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,已經比動物進化很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.68,0:13:37.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:41.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我還可以繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:43.78,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼能這麼努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.06,0:13:47.21,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,因為不想被她看見弱小的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:50.89,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,她要看 就要讓她看見帥氣的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:13:59.61,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人 是會長喜歡的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:01.42,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,白…才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.43,0:14:02.55,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你個戀愛腦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.81,0:14:04.91,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你就別遮遮掩掩了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:05.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,誰呀 是誰呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.98,0:14:06.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:08.15,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:09.52,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:20.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,做…做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:22.15,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,終於做到了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:24.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原書記 多虧你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:27.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真的太辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:29.44,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:31.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那 藤原書記
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:34.47,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來請教我怎麼墊球和接球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:48.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.02,0:14:50.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,白銀同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.67,0:14:59.58,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:03.49,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那個孩子是我培養的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:04.70,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你是媽媽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:09.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今日戰局 白銀和藤原的勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:10.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,白銀選手這次表現很好。
